      *
       JUSTIFY-FIELDS SECTION.
       JUST-000.
            IF F-CBFIRSTLINE = 7
                DIVIDE W-CALC BY 10 GIVING W-CALC.
            IF F-CBFIRSTLINE = 6
                DIVIDE W-CALC BY 100 GIVING W-CALC.
            IF F-CBFIRSTLINE = 5
                DIVIDE W-CALC BY 1000 GIVING W-CALC.
            IF F-CBFIRSTLINE = 4
                DIVIDE W-CALC BY 10000 GIVING W-CALC.
            IF F-CBFIRSTLINE = 3
                DIVIDE W-CALC BY 100000 GIVING W-CALC.
            IF F-CBFIRSTLINE = 2
                DIVIDE W-CALC BY 1000000 GIVING W-CALC.
            IF F-CBFIRSTLINE = 1
                DIVIDE W-CALC BY 10000000 GIVING W-CALC.
       JUST-999.
           EXIT.
